(8, '404 Not Found!', 'no-page-404', '<div class="oops"><h1>Oooops!! <span class="go-back"><a onclick="history.go(-1);" href="#">Go back</a>&nbsp; to the previous page</span></h1><div class="not-found"><div class="logo-img"><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/fox-logo.png'')}}" alt="Zendfox Logo" /></div><h2>404-Page Not Found!</h2><h3>Sorry, <span class="page-request">The page you requested was not found on server.</span></h3><h4>Suggestions:</h4><ul><li>Please make sure the spelling is correct.</li></ul></div></div>', 'one-column', '', '', '', 1, '2015-05-27 11:11:52', '2015-05-26 13:11:52'),
(9, 'FAQ', 'faq', '<div class="faq">\r\n    <div class="title_bar text-center"><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2></div>\r\n    <div class="questions">\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <h3>Ques.  Can I generate  multiple business codes on 1 PAN card no.?</h3>\r\n                <p class="ans">Ans. Yes but codes are restricted till 3 business codes with 1 PAN card no. </p>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <h3>Ques.  Is it mandatory to complete KYC form ?</h3>\r\n                <p class="ans">Ans. Yes </p>\r\n            </li>           \r\n            <li>\r\n                <h3>Ques.  From where, I can collect product ?</h3>\r\n                <p class="ans">Ans. You can collect your product from your senior or from company office. </p>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <h3>Ques. Can I convert rewards into cash?</h3>\r\n                <p class="ans">Ans. No you can not convert rewards into cash. </p>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <h3>Ques. What if I donâ€™t update my PAN no. details?</h3>\r\n                <p class="ans">Ans .  If you donâ€™t update your PAN no. details then payout deduction will be @ 20% as per govt. rule. </p>\r\n            </li>\r\n<li>\r\n                <h3>Ques. What if my immediate senior is not supporting me?</h3>\r\n                <p class="ans">Ans. You can walk in to the company office or write a mail on company mail id.</p>\r\n            </li>\r\n<li>\r\n                <h3>Ques. How can I enroll for company exclusive training programs?</h3>\r\n                <p class="ans">Ans.  You have to be in reward achiever list in order to enroll for that programme. </p>\r\n            </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'one-column', '', '', '', 1, '2015-05-27 11:48:08', '2015-06-04 07:33:29'),
(10, 'Know About Lucknow', 'know-about-lucknow', '<div class="know-about-lucknow">\r\n    <div class="title_bar text-center"><h2>Why invest in Lucknow</h2></div>     \r\n    <div class="clearfix tab-abou-lucknow" role="tabpanel">\r\n        <ul role="tablist" class="nav nav-tabs">\r\n            <li class="active" role="presentation"><a data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="home" href="#home">Know Your old Lucknow</a></li>\r\n            <li role="presentation"><a data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="profile" href="#profile">Know Your Today''s Lucknow</a></li>\r\n            <li role="presentation"><a data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="messages" href="#messages">Know Your''s Future Lucknow</a></li>           \r\n        </ul>\r\n        <div id="myCollapsible" class="tab-content clearfix">\r\n            <div id="home" class="tab-pane active clearfix" role="tabpanel">\r\n                <h4 class="panel-title">\r\n                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#old-lucknow" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">Know Your old Lucknow</a>\r\n                </h4>\r\n                <div id="old-lucknow" class="old-lucknow-img collapse clearfix">                    \r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/rumi-durwaza.jpg'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Rumi Gate</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/shah-najaf-imambara.jpg'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Imambara shahnajaf</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/Imambara.jpg'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Bada Imambara</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/clock-tower.jpg'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Clock Tower</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <p class="new-text">It is also known as the Golden City of East, Shiraz-i-Hind, Constantinople of the East and The city of Nawabs. Lucknow''s society is very famous for its etiquette and tradition which has attained a rare degree of sophistication. Be it the cultural charm or the architectural wonders, everything is well conserved here to make Lucknow "The city of many splendours". </p>\r\n                    <p class="new-text">Distance between Lucknow and New Delhi is 498 kms and it takes 5 hours 20 minutes by train, 7 hours by road and 45 minutes by air to reach Lucknow from New Delhi.Lucknow stands at an elevation of approximately 120 metres (390 ft) above mean sea level and covers an area of 689.1 sq. kms. (266.1 sq mi). It is the second largest city of northern India after New Delhi and the eleventh largest city of India. </p>\r\n                    <p class="new-text">It is surrounded on the eastern side by District Barabanki, on the western side by district Unnao, on the southern side by Raebareli and on the northern side by Sitapur and Hardoi. The city is on the northwestern shore of Gomti river, which flows through it. Lucknow is accessible from every part of India through air, rail and road. It is directly connected with New Delhi, Patna, Calcutta, Mumbai, Varanasi, Bangalore, Thiruvananthapuram, and other major cities by Amausi airport. The airport is suitable for all-weather operations and can provide parking facility up to 50 aircraft</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div id="profile" class="tab-pane clearfix" role="tabpanel">\r\n                <h4 class="panel-title">\r\n                    <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#today-lucknow" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">Know Your Today''s Lucknow</a>\r\n                </h4>\r\n                <div id="today-lucknow" class="old-lucknow-img collapse clearfix">\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/hazratganj.png'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Hazratganj</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/Walmart.png'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Walmart</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/AmbedkarPark.png'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Ambedkar park</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/shaheed-path.png'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>shaheed path</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>                \r\n                    <p class="new-text">Through extensive consultations with a variety of stakeholders, the Vision identified for Lucknow is - "One of the five most liveable cities in India where every citizen enjoys a high quality of life and access to basic services and amenities, and where local culture, crafts and heritage are preserved and promoted.</p>\r\n                    <p class="new-text">A city with a dynamic economy driven by service sectors such as knowledge-based education, health, tourism, and information technology that provides opportunities for all and makes it an attractive investment destination". The CDP offers a city assessment, a vision for the future development of the city and a three pronged strategy: infrastructure and service delivery improvement; basic services to the urban poor and institutional and governance reforms. </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div id="messages" class="tab-pane clearfix" role="tabpanel">\r\n                <h4 class="panel-title">                    \r\n                    <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#futurelucknow" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">Know Your''s Future Lucknow</a>\r\n                </h4>\r\n                <div id="futurelucknow" class="old-lucknow-img collapse clearfix">\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/International-Stadium.png'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>International stadium</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/IT-park.png'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>IT Park</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/Metro.png'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Metro Availability</h2></div>\r\n                    </div> \r\n                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 img-design">\r\n                        <a href="#" class="img">\r\n                            <img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/highway.png'')}}" alt="" />\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <div class="sub-name"><h2>Multinational Highway</h2></div>\r\n                    </div>                                    \r\n                    <h3>Lucknow Mahayojna</h3>\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                        <li>International stadium.</li>\r\n                        <li>Metro rail service.</li>\r\n                        <li>Multilevel hi-ways.</li>\r\n                        <li>International business hub.</li>\r\n                        <li>IT park.</li>\r\n                        <li>Cancer hospital.</li>\r\n                        <li>Biggest real estate projects.</li>\r\n                        <li>Educational center of India.</li>\r\n                        <li>Next metro city of India</li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>    \r\n</div>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">\r\n    $(''#myCollapsible'').collapse({\r\n  toggle: false\r\n});\r\n</script>', 'one-column', '', '', '', 1, '2015-05-28 14:47:22', '2015-06-04 05:53:37'),
(11, 'Business Plan', 'business-plan', '<div class="business-plan clearfix text-center">\r\n<div class="title_bar">\r\n<h2>Our Business Plan</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="concepts-work">\r\n<h3>Concepts work on</h3>\r\n<p>Systematic Distribution Network of E-Commerce + Real Estate</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 class="text-center product-price">Rs. 3300</h2>\r\n<div class="chart clearfix text-center">\r\n<h3>power package</h3>\r\n<div class="diagram"><span>includes</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="branded-shirts  clearfix">\r\n<div class="branded-shirts-pant col-md-6 col-xs-6">\r\n<div class="product-discription">\r\n<h4>&nbsp;<em class="fa fa-angle-double-right"></em> &nbsp; Branded Suitings &amp; Shirtings Raymond / Reid &amp; tailor(bond with the best) / Vimal or Gwalior(as per the availability)</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="real-estate-coupon col-md-6 col-xs-6">\r\n<div class="product-discription">\r\n<h4>&nbsp;<em class="fa fa-angle-double-right"></em> &nbsp;In BBW Whole Life if 1 plot sold then one can redeem infra coupon worth Rs. 6000 in cash / Cheque</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="title_bar">\r\n<h2>Types of Income</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class="types-income text-left">\r\n<li>Direct Income\r\n<p>- 500 INR/Direct</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Pair (Binary income) - Rs. 300/ pair\r\n<p>Capping - 6000/Day</p>\r\n<p>6000 x 30 days = 1,80,000 INR</p>\r\n<p>Closing - Per Day</p>\r\n<p>1st Pair = 1:2 or 2:1 = 1st payout</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Royalty Income\r\n<p>Eligibility Criteria:</p>\r\n<p>100 Pair - 10% of direct binary income</p>\r\n<p>250 pair - 25% of direct binary income</p>\r\n<p>500 pair - 50% of direct binary income</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Reward\r\n<p>20 Pair - Induction + Steam iron</p>\r\n<p>75 Pair - Android Phone</p>\r\n<p>175 Pair - 32&rsquo;&rsquo; LED</p>\r\n<p>350 Pair - Laptop</p>\r\n<p>800 Pair - Tata Nano 2015 (Next generation- red color)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Repurchase Infra income\r\n<p>Direct = 5% (On Booking, EMI, Final Payment)</p>\r\n<p>Binary = 4% (On Booking, EMI, Final Payment)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="title_bar">\r\n<h2>royalty calculation</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<table class="table data-table table-lists" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><colgroup> <col /> <col /> <col /> <col /> <col /> <col /> </colgroup>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td data-label="Sponsor">Sponsor</td>\r\n<td data-label="Direct Member">Direct Member</td>\r\n<td data-label="Binary Income">Binary Income</td>\r\n<td data-label="100 Pair">100 Pair</td>\r\n<td data-label="250 pair">250 pair</td>\r\n<td data-label="500 Pair">500 Pair</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mr.Z</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>10%</td>\r\n<td>25%</td>\r\n<td>50%</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="4">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>B</td>\r\n<td>6000</td>\r\n<td>600</td>\r\n<td>1500</td>\r\n<td>3000</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>C</td>\r\n<td>1000</td>\r\n<td>100</td>\r\n<td>250</td>\r\n<td>500</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>D</td>\r\n<td>2000</td>\r\n<td>200</td>\r\n<td>500</td>\r\n<td>1000</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>E</td>\r\n<td>2500</td>\r\n<td>250</td>\r\n<td>625</td>\r\n<td>1250</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tfoot>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>Daily Total</td>\r\n<td>11500</td>\r\n<td>1150</td>\r\n<td>2875</td>\r\n<td>5750</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>Monthly Total</td>\r\n<td>3,45,000</td>\r\n<td>34,500</td>\r\n<td>86,250</td>\r\n<td>1,72,500</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tfoot>\r\n</table>\r\n<div id="reward"><br /><br /></div>\r\n<div class="reward-system">\r\n<div class="title_bar text-center">\r\n<h2>Reward System</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<table class="table data-table">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Pair</td>\r\n<td>Reward Calculation: Cumulative</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>20 Pair</td>\r\n<td>Induction Cooktop + Steam Iron</td>\r\n<td><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/Induction.png'')}}" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>75 Pair</td>\r\n<td>Android Phone</td>\r\n<td><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/android-phone.png'')}}" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>175 Pair</td>\r\n<td>32&rsquo;&rsquo; LED</td>\r\n<td><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/led-tv.png'')}}" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>350 Pair</td>\r\n<td>Laptop</td>\r\n<td><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/laptop.png'')}}" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>800 Pair</td>\r\n<td>Tata Nano 2015 (Next generation)</td>\r\n<td><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/brooklyn/nano-car.png'')}}" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="repurchase-container">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n<div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 repurchase">\r\n<div class="title_bar text-left">\r\n<h2>Repurchase(Infra income)</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Example:</p>\r\n<ul class="text-left">\r\n<li>Project Name : Grand View</li>\r\n<li>rate : 550 Sq/ft</li>\r\n<li>Size of plot : 1000 sq/ft</li>\r\n<li>Total Amount: 1000 x 550 =550000/- INR</li>\r\n<li>Booking @ 10% - 5,50,000 x 10% = 55000</li>\r\n<li>Direct = 5% (On Booking, EMI, Final Payment)</li>\r\n<li>Binary = 4% (On Booking, EMI, Final Payment)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 projects-details">\r\n<div class="title_bar text-left">\r\n<h2>Projects</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Grand View - 550 Sq/Ft</p>\r\n<ul class="text-left">\r\n<ul class="text-left">\r\n<li>Satya Sai Vihar - Delivered</li>\r\n<li>Krishna Vihar Colony - Delivered</li>\r\n<li>Capital Sqaure - Delivered</li>\r\n<li>Hills Garden - Bhowali, Nainital</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="note">Developers - Landmark</p>\r\n<p class="note">Product : Studio Apartment (1 BHK, 2 BHK) flats</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\r\n    $(document).ready(function() {     \r\n  jQuery("body").addClass("business-plan_cms");        \r\n    });\r\n// ]]></script>', 'one-column', '', '', '', 1, '2015-05-29 17:40:22', '2015-07-06 05:35:02'),
(12, 'Welcome To Hamara Homes', 'home', '{{view key="home-banner" class="core/template" tpl="fox/html/banner"}}\r\n<div class="usp-sec text-center">\r\n    <div class="container">\r\n        <div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n                <h3 class="lined-heading"><span>We offer Services</span></h3>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-sm-3">\r\n                <div class="box-icon">\r\n                    <div class="circle"><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/stallion/business.png'')}}" alt="Business"/></div>\r\n                    <h4>Integrated Business Model</h4>\r\n                    <p>We have highly payable and integrated Business Model for earning and growing with the company.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class="col-sm-3">\r\n                <div class="box-icon">\r\n                    <div class="circle"><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/stallion/rates.png'')}}" alt="rates"/></div>\r\n                    <h4>Low Rates</h4>\r\n                    <p>We have comparatively low rates of the properties.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class="col-sm-3">\r\n                <div class="box-icon">      \r\n                    <div class="circle"><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/stallion/location.png'')}}" alt="location"/></div>\r\n                    <h4>Prime Location Sites</h4>\r\n                    <p>Our Site is in Prime Location in Center of The City. Nearest to Railway Station, Airport, &amp; Other Amnesties.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div  class="col-sm-3">\r\n                <div class="box-icon">\r\n                    <div class="circle"><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/stallion/quality.png'')}}" alt="quality"/></div>\r\n                    <h4>Quality &amp; Guranteed</h4>\r\n                    <p>Our Products have a quality and will satisfy you from all aspects.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="welcome-section">                \r\n    <div class="about">            \r\n        <div class="container">\r\n        <div class="about-top-bg">\r\n        <div class="row">\r\n        <div class="col-sm-4">\r\n            <div class="circle"><img src="{{themeUrl(''images/stallion/about.png'')}}" alt="About"/></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="col-sm-8">\r\n            <div class="inner-welcome"> \r\n                <h3 class="lined-heading">Welcome to <span>ABR Homes</span></h3>\r\n                <p>The A.B.R HOMES INDIA LTD. as a real estaet company is to develop and deliver unique,integrated lifestyle and work place environments through its focus on high quality services,strong project execution and our customer centric approach.Its Aim to develop integrated master planned communities which comprise residential projects along with one or more facilities,including retail andcommercial developments,school and hospital enabling a live, work and play theme with in the development.</p>\r\n                <p>We have the Expertise to always provide an appealing quality product, maintaining a high international standard. We envision the needs and desire of our clients, to provide them with a satisfying and enriching experience which goes beyond the actual product itself. </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>                \r\n        </div>                \r\n        </div>                \r\n        </div>                \r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">\r\n    $(document).ready(function() {\r\n        jQuery("body").addClass("home");\r\n    });\r\n</script>', 'one-column', '', '', '', 1, '2015-06-02 16:06:26', '2015-09-08 05:39:29'),
